data.enText: a tree or bush that has green leaves all through the year

data.chText: 经久不衰的罗西尼歌剧的重新制作
data.enText: a new production of Rossini's evergreen (= always popular) opera

tr: a plant having foliage that persists and remains green throughout the year
(of plants and shrubs) bearing foliage throughout the year

value.def: An evergreen is a tree or bush which has green leaves all the year round.

example.ex: Holly, like ivy and mistletoe, is an evergreen.
example.tran: 冬青和常春藤、槲寄生一样，都是常绿植物。

example.ex: Plant evergreen shrubs around the end of the month.
example.tran: 在月末前后种植常绿灌木。
